'''''Single and Married''''' ni filimi isekeje yasohotse muri 2012 ikorerwa muri [[Gana|Ghana]] na  [[Nigeriya|Nigeria]] , yakozwe na Yvonne Nelson afatanyije na  Pascal Amanfo. Irimo Yvonne Nelson, Chris Attoh, Nadia Buari, Tana Adelana, Kofi Adjorlolo, Eddie Watson na Jane 'Efya' Awindor .  Filime "yibanze ku ikinamico, amayeri n'amabanga mato yanduye y'inshuti eshatu z'abagabo, ubuzima bwabo bw'imibonano mpuzabitsina, kuba ingaragu cyangwa bashakanye. 

Iyi filime yahawe ibihembo icumi muri Gana Movie Awards 2012 kandi yegukana ibihembo bine muri ibyo birori, birimo Ishusho Nziza, Ubuyobozi Bwiza (Ururimi [[Icyongereza|rw'Icyongereza]]), Umukinnyi mwiza mu ruhare rwo gushyigikira ([[Icyongereza]]), na Sinema nziza. 

Urukurikirane, ''Ingaragu, Yubatse kandi rugoye'', rwasohotse mu 2014.  

== Umugambi ==
Jay ( Chris Attoh ), casanova, yatunguye inshuti ze, arasaba umukunzi we Kimora (Yvonne Nelson). Inshuti ya Jay, Raymond ( Kweku Elliot ) casanova ubu nawe yashakanye n'umwe mu nshuti za Kimora, Paula ( Nadia Buari ), ntabyitayeho. Andy (Eddie Watson), "mubi" muri batatu, atekereza ko Jay ari hafi gufungwa ubuzima bwe bwose.

Umwaka umwe nyuma yubukwe, Jay araryamana na Judith (Jane Awindor ), kandi ahora abeshya Kimora. Jay amaherezo aratandukana na we, kuko yamutunze cyane; asohoka mu nzu ye, Jay yikubita kuri Raymond, na we usohoka mu nzu ya nyirabuja, bityo amenya amabanga ya mugenzi we. Ikigaragara ni uko Paula, umunyamategeko, ahora ahugiye mu kazi kandi ntajya abona umwanya wa Raymond, mu gihe Kimora na we yanze guha Jay. Paula ahura Raymond na Yolanda (Itz Tiffany), inshuti ye ishaje, maze Raymond atangira gukundana nawe.

