== Kurekura ==
Iyi filime yerekana filime yasohotse kuri YouTube ku ya 25 Nyakanga 2012, kuri ubu ikaba imaze kubona miliyoni zigera ku icumi, ikaba imwe mu zerekanwa cyane na Nollywood.   Yasohotse muri [[Gana]] ku ya 22 Nzeri 2012,   yerekanwe bwa mbere muri Sinema ya Silverbird, Ikirwa cya Victoria, Lagos ku ya 28 Nzeri 2012. 

=== Ibihembo ===
'''''Single and Married i'''''fite ibihembo icumi muri Gana Movie Awards 2012, harimo Umukinnyi witwaye neza mu ruhare runini ([[Icyongereza]]) kuri Nelson, Umukinnyi mwiza mu nshingano zunganira ([[Icyongereza]]) kuri Attoh, Ishusho nziza - Ubufatanye bwa [[Afurika]], Guhindura neza, Ubuhanzi bwiza n'umuziki mwiza (Indirimbo y'umwimerere). Amaherezo yatsindiye Ishusho Nziza, Kuyobora neza (Ururimi rw'icyongereza), Umukinnyi mwiza mu nshingano zunganira ([[Icyongereza]]), na Sinema nziza.
